Photo is the key to let you know more before ordering, or eating any Chinese food. This app provides 400+ thumbnail photos for each dish, 400+ big detailed photo for each. 


For each dish, following information are given: 

--- 5 main categories: breakfast,vegetable,meat,soup and snack; 
--- table list show in each category; 
--- thumb photo for each dish; 
--- standard English name ; 
--- Chinese name and Pinyin; 
--- high quality detail photo; 

Why develop this application ? 

--- Help people to know more about real Chinese food. 

Who could use this application ? 

--- If you want to order carry out food from Chinese restaurants; 
--- If you travel to China; 
--- If you live in China and do not know much about Chinese; 


How to use ? 

--- Very easy to use, photo and English name can really help you. You can show the photo to Chinese waiters, or pronounce according to PinYIn.
